<h2 class="twikinetRoundedAttachments"><span class="twikinetHeader"><a name="Networking"></a> Networking </span></h2>
Both ports 9615 and 80 must be open.
<p />
<h2 class="twikinetRoundedAttachments"><span class="twikinetHeader"><a name="Networking_AN1"></a> Networking </span></h2>
<p />
on    
